{"tid":713810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[侵侵劇本流出]特朗普對華制裁參考《致命中國》","createTime":"2018-06-23T06:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T07:31:51.000Z","uid":1251,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"881e1a9de36df726f2f9ab3634daf7b93d49886c","tid":713810,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:45:51.000Z","msg":"【特朗普對華制裁參考《致命中國》】<br />\n【作者是白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅】<br />\n<br />\n中美兩國由關稅戰打到科技戰，有評論認為，特朗普對中國的制裁來得快、狠、準，其中對中興的禁令更被指是「一劍封喉」。<br />\n<br />\n重鎚出擊的背後，不少心水清的人發現，特朗普其實跟足劇本。<br />\n<br />\n2011年美國出版的書本《致命中國(Death by China)》狠批，中國操縱人民幣匯率，以掠奪性定價將外國競爭對手迫出市場，又大肆破壞環境，忽視工人的健康和安全。作者建議，美國政府縮小中美貿易逆差，對中國商品徵收45%關稅，甚至棄用中國商品，並且將中國列為匯率操控國。<br />\n<br />\n這些原本只是紙上談兵的建議，在特朗普上任後，逐一成為現實。對於一本書成為國策，不少人都沒有驚訝。因為今時今日，白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅，就是《致命中國》的作者。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅在《致命中國》強調，自己熱愛中國文化，跟很多中國人是好朋友，甚至在書中留下這句意味深長的說話。「獻給中國的朋友。希望他們終有一天能夠活得自由－－在那天來臨前，保重。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，如果內地人想知己知彼，從書中了解特朗普還有甚麼招式，恐怕就很難了，因為百度上是搜索不到這本書的。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#致命中國<br />\n#Deathbychina<br />\n#特朗普的對華劇本<br />\n#有線中國組弓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1756529907824821/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1756529907824821%2F&d=MmEE7c2Km%2FnVFkRvx4LWIRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=2437cf82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1756529907824821/</a>"},{"pid":"15b89af2cc7b8d9ea8e183ef29cff1db195e8e9a","tid":713810,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅，就是《致命中國》的作者。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9729bbe6b212df87226a0d6dd0ef8c43bbb0a8e","tid":713810,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"Peter Naverro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢youtube上面有一個death by China series類似documentary咁嘅片，好似係叫death by china,唔sure，不過一google就一定有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa7d811abaa3e333584864c20ff8dfd0a1f9d46","tid":713810,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9729bbe6b212df87226a0d6dd0ef8c43bbb0a8e","tid":713810,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"Peter Naverro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢youtube上面有一個death by China series類似documentary咁嘅片，好似係叫death by china,唔sure，不過一google就一定有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"個channel直頭叫death by china<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1cb98e3bf233591cb3ecde44fd71d1b5eb310e","tid":713810,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"本書拍埋電影大陸有得睇"},{"pid":"d04069609b327020f69fe0a7c55c4a1142341601","tid":713810,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e1cb98e3bf233591cb3ecde44fd71d1b5eb310e","tid":713810,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"本書拍埋電影大陸有得睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"竟然有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a8da45eedc21d1deb6dca0ff7a93c7d0dce81b","tid":713810,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78338f753931e1775e2be59f104f5bca012a4a18","tid":713810,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c12d0376a3229381c4112fc06b5e86cedbecd9","tid":713810,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"Summary from Wiki<br />\n<br />\n第一章標題為〈如果本書所言都是真的，那就不是在抨擊中國〉。本書認為，中共濫用貿易，「世界上人口最多的國家正迅速變成最大的經濟體，快速變成全球最厲害的刺客，不道德的中國企業家用致命的產品淹沒世界市場，中國採取非法保護主義，掠奪美國的產業和工作機會。」那法若認為，中美間貿易並不正常，而半數以上的中國優勢卻來自八項不公平的貿易手段，任何一項在自由貿易正常規則下都被明確禁止。本書詳盡論述，中國共產黨如何藉由八項「摧毀美國就業機會的武器」實踐經濟帝國主義：[6][7][8]<br />\n<br />\n詳細非法的貿易出口補貼網絡<br />\n巧妙操縱嚴重低估的貨幣<br />\n公然仿冒、盜版和徹底盜竊美國的智慧財產權<br />\n參與大規模環境破壞<br />\n極其寬鬆的工人健康和安全標準<br />\n非法進口關稅和配額<br />\n以掠奪性定價和做法將外國競爭對手擠出關鍵資源市場，然後以壟斷定價欺詐消費者<br />\n築起貿易保護主義長城，阻礙所有的外國競爭對手在中國設商戶<br />\n納瓦羅提出，美國應再次把人權視為外交政策的核心價值。本書最後一章提出了一整套建議：個人選擇方案、企業管理層決策、政府的政策措施。其中例如，包括推動國會立法，要求與美國進行自由貿易的任何國家，須放棄所有非法出口補貼，貨幣匯率需反映實況、嚴格的智慧財產權保護，符合國際規規範的環境保護及健康與安全標準，開放能源和原材料的全球進出口市場、提供「包括媒體和網際網路服務在內的自由與開放的國內市場」，等等。[8]"},{"pid":"156a36f8cc95a37c74d3d63babc4db91c71667e4","tid":713810,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04069609b327020f69fe0a7c55c4a1142341601","tid":713810,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e1cb98e3bf233591cb3ecde44fd71d1b5eb310e","tid":713810,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"本書拍埋電影大陸有得睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"竟然有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"佢仲有幾本書《致命中國》講經濟，《臥虎》講中國軍力點樣威脅到美國"},{"pid":"8eb33aae752dec722c79532eee43b3884a637bc4","tid":713810,"uid":17081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/DnJRRO5L4wX60/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FDnJRRO5L4wX60%2Fgiphy.gif&h=81f8a4c4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}